    {
      "id": "sybil_20_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_20",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my reliable ride and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape and has been super well-maintained, so it's ready to hit the road for its next big adventure! It looks great, runs smoothly, and is just waiting for a new owner to enjoy it as much as I have. If you\u2019re looking for a dependable car that still feels fresh, this is the one for you!",
