      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six powerplant. This unit retains its high-revving character with crisp throttle response via individual throttle bodies. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement, addressing common chassis fatigue points. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission shifts with mechanical precision, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with enthusiastic use, the suspension geometry remains tight, utilizing refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. A true mechanical specimen for the purist looking for a sorted chassis.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Well-maintained engine. Clean interior. Recent service completed. Reliable daily driver.",
