    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_18_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_18",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained sedan offers a perfect blend of performance and comfort. The exterior shines in a classic metallic finish, showing only minor road wear consistent with careful ownership. Inside, the leather upholstery remains supple and free of tears, complemented by a smoke-free cabin and fully functional dual-zone climate control. Mechanically, the car is sound; it has undergone regular oil changes and a recent brake service, ensuring a smooth and responsive driving experience. All electronics, including the premium sound system and navigation, work perfectly. With a clean title and comprehensive service records, this vehicle is ready for its next journey.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
