    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for all my daily commutes and weekend trips. It\u2019s got a little bit of character from being enjoyed, but it still runs like a dream and is totally ready for its next adventure! If you\u2019re looking for a reliable car that still looks fantastic on the road, this is definitely the one for you. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 34500.0,
