    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit maintains excellent compression across all cylinders and benefits from a recent VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement\u2014essential preventive maintenance for the chassis. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal power delivery. Suspension geometry remains tight with upgraded polyurethane bushings. While the Alpine White finish shows minor road rash commensurate with its mileage, the aerodynamic integrity and cooling system performance remain uncompromised. A driver-focused example ready for spirited B-road sessions or track-day duty.",
